      <title>德克萨斯州市政借款人哀叹限制银行的反 ESG 法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/texas-muni-borrowers-bemoan-anti-esg-laws-restricting-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州的借款人聚集在一次行业会议上，对该州的两项共和党支持的法律表示遗憾，发行人称这些法律限制了他们可以与哪些华尔街银行开展业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/texas-muni-borrowers-bemoan-anti-esg-laws-restricting-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:26:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗在袭击后切断了委内瑞拉与厄瓜多尔的外交关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/maduro-cuts-venezuela-s-diplomatic-ties-with-ecuador-after-raid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗表示，由于厄瓜多尔本月袭击墨西哥大使馆，他将切断与厄瓜多尔所有剩余的外交关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/maduro-cuts-venezuela-s-diplomatic-ties-with-ecuador-after-raid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:55:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
